         <p id="answer4" class="answers">
            Light a life promotes positive mental health and wellbeing to all individuals and communities, and through our network of Mental Health Associations, we support people who experience mental health difficulties on their journey of recovery.
            Light a life's vision is for an Ireland where mental health is valued as being an essential part of personal wellbeing and the health of the nation. MHI will lead the way in informing Irish societyâ€™s understanding of mental health and fostering a culture where people with mental health difficulties are respected and supported.
